(29833, 'Healthy rose 200 ml feminine wash', 'هيلثي روز غسول سيدات 200 مل', '', '65', 'Chlorhexidine -menthol-thyme extract-chamomile extract -tea tree oil-glycerine', 'Blu care', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Feminine wash', '200 ml', 'Chlorhexidine is available over-the-counter in various formulations (e.g. solution, sponge, cloth, swab) as a topical antiseptic to sanitize prior to surgeries and/or medical procedures.[L11518,L11521,L11527,L11533] Dental formulations, available by prescription only, include an oral rinse indicated for the treatment of gingivitis[L11512] and a slow-release "chip" which is inserted into periodontal pockets and is indicated for the reduction of pocket depth in adult patients with periodontitis as an adjunct therapy to dental scaling and root planing procedures.[L11536]', '', '', 762, '2024-07-18', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
